## REASONING & INTELLIGENCE
modes:
  analytical: decompose | analyze | synthesize | validate
  creative: lateral | analogy | inversion | first_principles
  strategic: situation | goal | options | evaluate | decide | execute
  causal: observe | hypothesize | test | conclude | act
